34:08.271 --> 34:10.537
Show her some thigh.

34:11.879 --> 34:12.913
Bleacher!

34:12.913 --> 34:14.277
It’s overflowing now.

34:14.277 --> 34:16.180
Get in there. Back to work.
- All right.

34:16.180 --> 34:17.577
It’s up to me ankles!

34:17.577 --> 34:19.480
- Time-waster.

34:19.480 --> 34:21.185
- Bleacher!

34:21.185 --> 34:24.221
Curse that idle peasant.

34:32.559 --> 34:34.495
What you got there?

34:34.495 --> 34:36.233
Nothing.

34:36.299 --> 34:39.203
Do you like that coop, Noodle?

34:39.203 --> 34:39.973
All right.

34:39.973 --> 34:43.306
I was collecting laundry
from Professor Monocle
the other day.

34:43.306 --> 34:44.010
Yeah.

34:44.010 --> 34:46.540
He’s writing a book about
the Bavarian Royal Family.

34:46.540 --> 34:47.211
Boring.

34:47.211 --> 34:49.950
He’s got sketches of noblemen
all over his wall.

34:49.950 --> 34:50.412
So?

34:50.412 --> 34:53.283
This one
looked rather familiar.

34:54.647 --> 34:55.318
Oh.

34:55.318 --> 34:57.958
Blow me.
That looks exactly like...

34:57.958 --> 34:59.289
Mr. Bleacher.

34:59.289 --> 35:03.557
Are you telling me Bleacher
is a Bavarian aristocrat?

35:03.557 --> 35:05.361
- Uh-huh.

35:05.361 --> 35:07.330
Go and get my gin.

35:08.397 --> 35:10.168
♪ First,
