47:55.295 --> 47:57.935
I have water in my ears.

47:58.100 --> 47:58.936
Oh.

47:58.936 --> 48:00.773
Yeah, that... You’ve...

48:00.773 --> 48:03.072
Okay, that makes sense. Yeah.

48:03.072 --> 48:05.140
Listen, I’m sorry.

48:05.140 --> 48:06.713
I’m all outta whack.

48:06.713 --> 48:09.309
Truth is, I don’t wanna
